    <item>
      <title>波音公司考虑通过出售股票筹集至少 100 亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/boeing-said-to-weigh-raising-at-least-10-billion-selling-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，波音公司正考虑通过发行新股筹集至少 100 亿美元，以补充因持续罢工而进一步耗尽的现金储备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/boeing-said-to-weigh-raising-at-least-10-billion-selling-stock</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 10:08:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
